<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gray Layout</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        /* Header */
        header {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Container for sidebar and main content */
        .container {
            display: flex;
            min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
        }

        /* Sidebar */
        aside {
            width: 250px;
            background-color: #4d4d4d;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: inset 1px 0 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        aside ul {
            list-style: none;
        }

        aside ul li {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }

        aside ul li a {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        aside ul li a:hover {
            color: white;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        /* Main content */
        main {
            flex: 1;
            background-color: #e8e8e8;
            padding: 30px;
        }

        main h2 {
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .content-box {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .content-box h3 {
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .content-box p {
            color: #000000;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Footer */
        footer {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #aaaaaa;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #000000;
        }

        footer p {
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        /* Responsive design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            aside {
                width: 100%;
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            main {
                padding: 15px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header -->
    <header>
        <h1>Gray Layout Design</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- Main Container -->
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#services">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="#portfolio">Portfolio</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </aside>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main>
            <h2>Welcome to Gray Layout</h2>
            
            <div class="content-box">
                <h3>Section 1</h3>
                <p>
                    This is a responsive gray layout design. The color scheme uses various shades of gray to create a professional and modern appearance. The layout includes a header, sidebar navigation, main content area, and footer.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-box">
                <h3>Section 2</h3>
                <p>
                    The layout is fully responsive and will adapt to different screen sizes. On mobile devices, the sidebar moves above the main content area for better usability.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-box">
                <h3>Section 3</h3>
                <p>
                    You can easily customize the colors and content to match your specific needs. This template provides a solid foundation for building professional websites.
                </p>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Gray Layout Design. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
